---
import MacOSDemo from './demo/MacOSDemo.astro';
---

<section id="demo" class="demo-hide-narrow-portrait scroll-mt-16 overflow-visible px-[1vw] py-[1vh]">
  <div class="demo-section-frame">
    <MacOSDemo />

    <aside class="demo-section-copy" id="demo-section-copy" aria-label="演示说明">
      <div class="demo-copy-accent" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <p class="demo-copy-label">在线体验</p>
      <h2 class="demo-copy-title">
        亲手试试
        <span class="text-gradient-brand">Origami</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="demo-copy-lead">
        把多个 macOS 窗口合并成组，在窗口外叠加标签栏——像切换浏览器标签一样，快速、无痕地切换。
      </p>

      <ol class="demo-guide-steps" id="demo-guide-steps">
        <li class="demo-guide-step is-active" data-step="0">
          <span class="demo-guide-num">01</span>
          <div class="demo-guide-body">
            <p class="demo-guide-title">拖动标签</p>
            <p class="demo-guide-desc">按住窗口外的标签，拖向另一个窗口</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="demo-guide-step" data-step="1">
          <span class="demo-guide-num">02</span>
          <div class="demo-guide-body">
            <p class="demo-guide-title">拖入合并</p>
            <p class="demo-guide-desc">释放在目标窗口上，合并为同一组</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="demo-guide-step" data-step="2">
          <span class="demo-guide-num">03</span>
          <div class="demo-guide-body">
            <p class="demo-guide-title">点击切换</p>
            <p class="demo-guide-desc">在标签栏点击，即时切换组内窗口</p>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .demo-section-frame {
    position: relative;
    width: 85vw;
    max-width: 1000px;
    height: min(72vh, 640px);
    margin: 0 auto;
    overflow: visible;
    --demo-copy-ratio: 28%;
    --demo-zone-gap: 20px;
  }

  .demo-section-copy {
    position: absolute;
    right: var(--demo-zone-gap);
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    z-index: 1;
    width: calc(var(--demo-copy-ratio) - var(--demo-zone-gap));
    max-height: 88%;
    padding: 0 clamp(0.5rem, 1vw, 1rem);
    background: none;
    border: none;
    box-shadow: none;
    overflow-y: auto;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .demo-section-copy > * {
    pointer-events: auto;
  }

  .demo-copy-accent {
    width: 2.5rem;
    height: 3px;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00d4ff, #0099cc, #0056b3);
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .demo-copy-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #0099cc;
  }

  .demo-copy-title {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 1.85vw, 1.625rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.25;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: #0f172a;
  }

  .demo-copy-lead {
    margin-top: 0.65rem;
    font-size: clamp(0.8125rem, 1vw, 0.9375rem);
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: #475569;
  }

  .demo-guide-steps {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: clamp(0.85rem, 1.5vh, 1.25rem) 0 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.45rem;
  }

  .demo-guide-step {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.85rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    border-left: 2px solid transparent;
    padding-left: 0.75rem;
    transition:
      border-color 0.35s ease,
      opacity 0.35s ease;
  }

  .demo-guide-step.is-active {
    border-left-color: #00b7eb;
  }

  .demo-guide-step:not(.is-active) {
    opacity: 0.55;
  }

  .demo-guide-num {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: #0099cc;
    opacity: 0.7;
    padding-top: 0.15rem;
    transition: opacity 0.35s ease, color 0.35s ease;
  }

  .demo-guide-step.is-active .demo-guide-num {
    opacity: 1;
    color: #007bb8;
  }

  .demo-guide-title {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #0f172a;
  }

  .demo-guide-desc {
    margin-top: 0.2rem;
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: #64748b;
  }

  .demo-guide-step.is-active .demo-guide-title {
    color: #0369a1;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .demo-section-frame {
      --demo-copy-ratio: 100%;
      width: 92vw;
      height: min(78vh, 620px);
    }

    .demo-section-copy {
      right: 10px;
      left: 10px;
      top: auto;
      bottom: 10px;
      transform: none;
      width: auto;
      max-height: 42%;
    }
  }
</style>
